{"tid":712027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天津再爆]全國人大常委會:天津濱海新區經濟數據虛報率達56%","createTime":"2018-06-21T23:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T00:42:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"57950ad74f7fd031ca24d8bc22195a3ba7779ffd","tid":712027,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:54:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1755011954643283/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1755011954643283%2F&d=afgieTsPw%2F151FGscSvHi2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=3cc707bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1755011954643283/</a><br />\n<br />\n【全國人大常委會:天津濱海新區經濟數據虛報率達56%】<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會在星期三的會議上公布檢查企業統計數字的報告，點名提到三個地方的違法企業的平均虛報率，其中天津濱海新區臨港經濟區有56%企業有虛報數字，即是超過一半企業的業績都是假的。<br />\n<br />\n造假數據是去年發現的，今年數據是怎樣呢? 天津市統計局公布1至4月份的經濟數據，幾乎滿江紅，跟去年同期相比，投資和基建項目都在跌， 幅度有30%-60%。<br />\n<br />\n至於全國其他地方又如何呢? 國家統計局核查全國2000多間出現異常數據的企業和接近3000個固定資產投資項目，發現有超過一半的公司和九成項目的資料有編造數據，有些虛報倍數還很高。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出統計造假、弄虛作假屢禁不止，責任在於個別幹部上。主要因為地方政府搞攀比、爭排名，制定脫離現實的目標，還層層加碼，甚至直接向企業下達任務，當任務難以完成時就造假數。<br />\n<br />\n除了要求企業按指定目標填報，還代他們填報。目的是為了升級考核，爭取融資、騙稅逃稅等。<br />\n<br />\n檢查組提出要解決問題必需先提高統計部門的執法地位，因為工作人員到地區進行檢查時，常遭到地方政府阻礙或拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n#弄虛作假<br />\n#數據造假<br />\n#水份<br />\n#天津<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"c9b1697881907166ce4e76716dea1707b3916f01","tid":712027,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:00:50.000Z","msg":"其他44%查唔到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52f7d327b5d0cf876d4c8ccaee2ca60508159dc","tid":712027,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9b1697881907166ce4e76716dea1707b3916f01","tid":712027,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:00:50.000Z","msg":"其他44%查唔到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:11:00.000Z","msg":"去左美國點查姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5719b838ea67040d746a5f3ccf4029264a1d5f","tid":712027,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c341afad20198bb77e3b90172ed7b4ce13c441","tid":712027,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:14:44.000Z","msg":"支爆未"},{"pid":"4ec5f293ada75e07794fa1916b66493ccecf8676","tid":712027,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:15:15.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"e1e081561f097e2a3e6ac8944e0306fa292c0fc3","tid":712027,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"無可能 假新聞"},{"pid":"7627461bf969bf624a2bceb4c51b54421842b2e9","tid":712027,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:25:57.000Z","msg":"560％先真下ma <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870f52844c52757a804240ec40714c30123746f7","tid":712027,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:38:00.000Z","msg":"濱海新區大爆炸完唔跌先奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45392375312b847ec02c5c01023a2d9aa43776d","tid":712027,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:40:11.000Z","msg":"報假都報左幾十年<br />\n咪又繼續歌舞昇平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00156546d6ab1121eb4384a99ca0e20eb59ca17f","tid":712027,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"啲會計師核數師錢已袋走人"},{"pid":"b4e1d1df90d66639cdeb33da139badea69bb94dc","tid":712027,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},